# Fishing fleet	names (delimited with spaces; no spaces in names)
TCF #--directed Tanner crab fishery
SCF #--bycatch in snow crab fishery
RKF #--bycatch in BBRKC fishery
GF_All #--bycatch in groundfish undetermined gear fisheries
# Survey names (delimited with spaces; no spaces in names)
NMFS  #--NMFS survey, indices for undetermined males, immature females, mature females
